               <p>I was going up <placeName id="t17760710-6-crimeloc25">Holborn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17760710-6-crimeloc25" type="placeName" value="Holborn"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17760710-6-crimeloc25" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17760710-6-off23 t17760710-6-crimeloc25"></join> on Sunday night the 7th of July, at near ten o'clock; I felt a tug at my pocket; I turned about, and the prisoner had my handkerchief half out of my pocket; I went to lay hold of him, upon which he snatched my handkerchief out, and ran away; I pursued him, and took him just as he was going to turn down Field-lane; I never lost sight of him, and I am sure he is the man. I did not find my handkerchief.</p>
               <p>The prisoner said nothing in his defence.</p>
